# 止蝕  
(pos:動詞)  
<explanation>  
yue:投資或交易時，為咗防止損失進一步擴大而主動沽出資產，使虧損「停住」；即係「割肉」嘅委婉說法（常見於股市、期貨等金融語境）  
eng:to cut losses (e.g. by selling an asset to prevent further decline in value); to stop further loss  
<eg>  
yue:呢隻股票跌到咁犀利，再唔止蝕真係會蝕到傾家盪產！ (ni1 zi2 gau1 pip3 dik1 dou3 si3 lei6, zoi3 m4 zi2 sik1 zan1 si6 wui2 sik1 dou3 king1 gaa1 dong3 caan2!)  
eng:This stock’s falling so fast—if we don’t cut our losses now, we’ll end up ruined!  

yue:老手通常會設好止蝕點，一到就即刻沽出，唔會感情用事。 (lou5 sau3 tung1 wui2 si6 hou3 zi2 sik1 dim2, jat1 dou3 zau6 kap1 luk6 seot3, m4 wui5 gam2 cyun2 jung6 si6.)  
eng:Experienced traders usually set stop-loss points in advance and sell immediately once hit—no emotional decisions. [end of text]


